all the scales associated
with our universe

00:44:27.880 --> 00:44:30.180
to where they are right now.

00:44:30.180 --> 00:44:30.680
OK.

00:44:30.680 --> 00:44:37.240
Having done this, I'm
going to define a of t

00:44:37.240 --> 00:44:43.923
