00:44:43.923 --> 00:44:45.340
For dimensional
reasons, I'm going

00:44:45.340 --> 00:44:49.750
to need to put this into
my radial coordinate.

00:44:49.750 --> 00:44:51.180
So notice, what's
going on here is

00:44:51.180 --> 00:44:54.300
that my R will now have
